  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to compare the rate of healing, the infection or
      complication rate, pain perception and scarring from burn injuries using two types of burn
      dressings.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate AWBAT™ compared to Biobrane® for the treatment of
      superficial partial-thickness burns using the patient as their own control.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
